    <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-x-8 gap-y-2 font-display font-bold text-sm tracking-widest" style="color:#1A1A1A;text-transform:uppercase;font-family:'Barlow Condensed',sans-serif">
      <span>Oldsmar, FL</span><span style="color:#E6A817">·</span><span>CCC1337380</span><span style="color:#E6A817">·</span><span>HappyRoof.com</span><span style="color:#E6A817">·</span><span style="color:#3B9FD9">(813) 595-7663</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- WHY SECTION -->
<section class="py-20" style="background:#FFFFFF">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-5">
    <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-14 items-start">
      <div>
        <p class="sl gt mb-3">Why Choose Your Local Roofer</p>
        <h2 style="font-family:'Barlow Condensed',sans-serif;font-weight:800;font-size:clamp(2rem,4vw,3rem);line-height:.95;color:#1A1A1A;letter-spacing:-.01em;margin-bottom:1.5rem">WHY OLDSMAR HOMEOWNERS CHOOSE THEIR NEIGHBORHOOD ROOFER</h2>
        <p style="color:#555555;font-size:1rem;line-height:1.75;margin-bottom:1.5rem">When a roof leak develops or a storm rips shingles off your Oldsmar home, the last thing you want is to wait for a contractor based an hour away. Happy Roof is headquartered at 141 Stevens Avenue in Oldsmar - we are literally your neighbor. That means faster response times, quicker emergency tarping, and a team that knows the specific roofing challenges Oldsmar homes face.</p>
        <p style="color:#555555;font-size:1rem;line-height:1.75;margin-bottom:1.5rem">Oldsmar sits along the northern shore of Old Tampa Bay, where afternoon thunderstorms roll in from the Gulf and Tampa Bay creates its own localized weather patterns. Homes near Mobbly Bay Preserve and along Shore Drive experience higher salt air exposure than properties farther inland near Race Track Road. The city's mix of 1960s-era concrete block homes, 1990s subdivisions in Westwood Lakes, and newer builds near Veterans Memorial Park means our crews see every type of roofing issue - from aging shingle failure to tile displacement to metal panel corrosion.</p>
        <p style="color:#555555;font-size:1rem;line-height:1.75;margin-bottom:1.5rem">We provide honest assessments on every Oldsmar roof repair. If a targeted repair will extend your roof's life for years, that is what we recommend. If the damage reveals deeper problems that make replacement more sensible, we explain why. Visit our <a href="/oldsmar-roofing" style="color:#3B9FD9;text-decoration:none;font-weight:600">Oldsmar roofing page</a> or our <a href="/roof-repair" style="color:#3B9FD9;text-decoration:none;font-weight:600">roof repair page</a> for more information.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="space-y-4">
        <div class="scard p-6">
          <div class="check"><div class="check-dot"><svg width="10" height="10" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#E6A817" stroke-width="3"><path d="M20 6L9 17l-5-5"/></svg></div><div><strong style="font-family:'Barlow Condensed',sans-serif;font-weight:700;font-size:1.05rem">Fastest Response in Oldsmar</strong><p style="color:#555555;font-size:.9rem;line-height:1.6;margin-top:.25rem">Our office is in Oldsmar. When you call with an emergency, our crews do not have to drive across the bay - we can be on-site quickly for emergency tarping and assessment.</p></div></div>
        </div>
        <div class="scard p-6">
          <div class="check"><div class="check-dot"><svg width="10" height="10" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#E6A817" stroke-width="3"><path d="M20 6L9 17l-5-5"/></svg></div><div><strong style="font-family:'Barlow Condensed',sans-serif;font-weight:700;font-size:1.05rem">Storm Damage Repair</strong><p style="color:#555555;font-size:.9rem;line-height:1.6;margin-top:.25rem">Oldsmar's bayfront location means exposure to tropical storm and hurricane winds. We repair all wind, rain, and debris damage and help with insurance documentation.</p></div></div>
        </div>
        <div class="scard p-6">
          <div class="check"><div class="check-dot"><svg width="10" height="10" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#E6A817" stroke-width="3"><path d="M20 6L9 17l-5-5"/></svg></div><div><strong style="font-family:'Barlow Condensed',sans-serif;font-weight:700;font-size:1.05rem">Flashing & Seal Repairs</strong><p style="color:#555555;font-size:.9rem;line-height:1.6;margin-top:.25rem">Deteriorated flashing around chimneys, skylights, and pipe boots is the most common repair we perform on Oldsmar homes. We replace with durable, code-compliant materials.</p></div></div>
        </div>
        <div class="scard p-6">
          <div class="check"><div class="check-dot"><svg width="10" height="10" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#E6A817" stroke-width="3"><path d="M20 6L9 17l-5-5"/></svg></div><div><strong style="font-family:'Barlow Condensed',sans-serif;font-weight:700;font-size:1.05rem">Honest Repair Recommendations</strong><p style="color:#555555;font-size:.9rem;line-height:1.6;margin-top:.25rem">We are your neighbors - our reputation in Oldsmar matters to us. We give you a straight answer about whether your roof needs a repair, monitoring, or replacement.</p></div></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
