        </div>
        <h3 style="font-family:'Barlow Condensed',sans-serif;font-weight:800;font-size:1.35rem;color:#1A1A1A;margin-bottom:.75rem">Shingle Replacement</h3>
        <p style="color:#555555;font-size:.95rem;line-height:1.7">Wind-lifted, cracked, or missing shingles are the most frequent repair on Oldsmar homes. We match existing shingle color and style for a seamless result.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="scard p-8">
