        </div>
        <h3 style="font-family:'Barlow Condensed',sans-serif;font-weight:800;font-size:1.35rem;color:#1A1A1A;margin-bottom:.75rem">Pipe Boot & Vent Seal Replacement</h3>
        <p style="color:#555555;font-size:.95rem;line-height:1.7">Rubber pipe boots dry out and crack in Florida's sun, creating slow leaks that damage ceilings and insulation. We replace them with durable, long-lasting alternatives.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="scard p-8">
        <div style="width:52px;height:52px;border-radius:14px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;background:rgba(230,168,23,.1);margin-bottom:1rem">
          <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#E6A817" stroke-width="2"><path d="M22 11.08V12a10 10 0 1 1-5.93-9.14"/><polyline points="22 4 12 14.01 9 11.01"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 style="font-family:'Barlow Condensed',sans-serif;font-weight:800;font-size:1.35rem;color:#1A1A1A;margin-bottom:.75rem">Soffit, Fascia & Gutter Repair</h3>
        <p style="color:#555555;font-size:.95rem;line-height:1.7">Heavy Oldsmar rainstorms can damage gutters and cause water to back up into soffits and fascia. We repair or replace damaged components to protect your roof edge.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- OUR PROCESS -->
<section class="py-20" style="background:#FFFFFF">
